{{Top|leg}}
The '''Morath''' were a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] found near the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]]: their name was probably connected to that of the [[Morath Nebula/Legends|Morath Nebula]].

Under the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], they established two [[Mining/Legends|mining]] colonies a little way inside the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]], on the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] of [[Elcorth]] and [[Kojash]]. Both colonies were wiped out during the [[Yevethan Purge|Great Purge]] by the [[Yevetha]].

A few survivors were apparently taken as hostages, such as [[Jara ba Nylra]] and [[Liekas Tendo]]. However, [[Enara]], who claimed to have been a [[pholikite]] miner on Elcorth, was actually a [[Fallanassi/Legends|Fallanassi]].

